description:
On November 23rd, Nourish in collaboration with @mame_mcgill and @ceusmcgill will host a cooking competition!!

Create your teams and sign up to participate 🥦🥕🥒🍅🥑🌶️🌽

You won’t want to miss it!!! Food, drinks, and music will be at the final location for the judging session...🪩

Hey Guys 🍁! We are back this Saturday with a 5k charity run at Mount Royal parc in collaboration with @mcgillstudentsrunningclub ! Tickets are $5 and all proceeds will be donated to La Maison Bleue. We’re excited to see you all and have a fun time while helping a cause ! Tickets in bio !☀️
